_SLOT:CTA --><p><a class=\"button primary is-large\" href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/free-newcastle-business-audit/\">Get Online Ordering Audit</a></p><p>Related: <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/pos-setup-newcastle/\">POS Setup Newcastle</a> | <a href=\"https://newcastlehub.info/restaurant-solutions/\">Restaurant Solutions</a></p><!-- /AI_SLOT:CTA --><!-- AI_SLOT:SCHEMA --><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can online ordering work with my current POS?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Usually yes. We map product structure, modifiers, taxes, and pickup rules to reduce double handling.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do I need a mobile app?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"No. Most businesses start with a fast mobile web ordering flow and optional QR entry points.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How quickly can this go live?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Simple setups can go live quickly after menu cleanup, payment setup, and test-order validation.\"}}]}</script><!-- /AI_SLOT:SCHEMA --></div></div></div></div></div></section>\n",
